  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been abducted into a underground facility where doctors are doing disturbing genetic modification experiments on people, but something has gone wrong and you have a chance to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.mp4?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay revolves around fighting different monsters the lab has created with guns. Lots of running away and shooting. You can play in first person and third person. You can also upgrade your skills with xp you get from killing monsters or doing side quests. The further you get the more you will discover about the lab and the monsters in it. Do you have what it takes to escape? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.mp4?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >this game now supports controllers and keyboard</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been abducted into a underground facility where doctors are doing disturbing genetic modification experiments on people, but something has gone wrong and you have a chance to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.mp4?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gameplay revolves around fighting different monsters the lab has created with guns. Lots of running away and shooting. You can play in first person and third person. You can also upgrade your skills with xp you get from killing monsters or doing side quests. The further you get the more you will discover about the lab and the monsters in it. Do you have what it takes to escape? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras